  "Description": {
    "English": "Adds <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Terrain Manipulation</span> capability to the laser systems of the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Nautilon Submarine</span>.<br><br>Cooled by specially designed water intakes, it is specifically calibrated to carve through the complex geology of the sea floor.",
